 ♫ Beyond sight ♫ 

162
00:16:24,947 --> 00:16:27,752
 ♫ Your silhouette is so gentle ♫ 

163
00:16:28,928 --> 00:16:32,686
 ♫ The world is spinning ♫ 

164
00:16:34,464 --> 00:16:37,950
 ♫ The breeze is shouting ♫ 

